Revision history for Lingua-Thesaurus


0.09 08.05.2014
  - fixed problem with unbalanced parens in a MATCH query
  - force dependency on v1.39 of DBD::SQLite

0.08 06.06.2013
  - better doc for internal/external relations
  - bug fix: fetch_term_id() and related() did not return origins

0.07 05.06.2013
  - search_terms() and fetch_term() can filter on $origin
  - more tests for SA and SN relations

0.06 20.05.2013
  - allow same term to be loaded from several origins
  - fix some parsing bugs

0.05 03.05.2013
  - new field "origin" to tag which thesaurus a term comes from
  - accept single wildcard '?' in searches

0.04 21.02.2013
  - LivelinkCollectionServer: use :crlf perlio for better support of DOS format
  - do not call Moose::Meta::Class->create(..) if class already exists

0.03 21.02.2013
  - LivelinkCollectionServer: accept input file in DOS format, even on Unix

0.02 19.02.2013
  - fixed test data format
  - fixed missing dependency on Search::Tokenizer

0.01 17.02.2012
  - first CPAN release

